name: Tractor
description: A tractor is a powerful vehicle designed to perform heavy-duty tasks in agriculture and construction.

name: Trolly
description: A trolley is a wheeled cart or vehicle used to transport items or passengers, often powered by electricity in public transit or used for carrying goods in various settings.

name: Cultivator
description: A cultivator is a tool used to loosen soil and control weeds before planting.

name: Wheat thresher
description: A wheat-thresher is a machine that separates wheat grains from stalks and chaff during harvest.

name: Wheel Hand
description: A wheel hand tractor is a compact, manually-operated machine with wheels, designed for small-scale farming tasks like tilling, plowing, and cultivating.

name: Compass
description: A wheat cutting compass machine is an agricultural tool designed to precisely cut wheat stalks at a uniform height, ensuring a consistent and efficient harvest.
